topic.title: ZeroHello all buttons unresponsive. No menus pop-up
topic.body:
I have a node that was working fine, but now on ZeroHello none of the menus (like trackers, Tor, Port or any of the site sub menu accessed through the three little buttons) will open. I can open sites and they work fine, just can't get to any menus on ZeroHello. 

Tried multiple browsers. 

Single error in browser console goes :
`Uncaught TypeError: Cannot read property 'date_added' of undefined
    at FeedList.render (all.js?lang=en&site_modified=1562292014:2758)
    at Array.<anonymous> (all.js?lang=en&site_modified=1562292014:2189)
    at doRender (all.js?lang=en&site_modified=1562292014:920)`

Related?
